Summary: It was silver/grey oval shaped object that was moving east, then stopped, then dissappeared.
divs: sighting detailsi saw the object the second time at aprox. 1:15pm on feb 12 2009 from my office window on the top\third floor.something told me to look out,so i did and i saw this object heading west into a cloud, then out, then did a zig-zag motion and went into reverse, then forward towards west again, going into a cloud and never coming out of it.
